[[["compound", "nummod", "compound", "cc", "conj", "acl"], "Unit 6  Positive Thinking and Happier Living."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "compound", "nmod", "case", "nsubj", "compound", "compound", "compound", "nmod", "case", "nmod:tmod", "det", "cc", "conj"], "During the spring semester of 2006, Harvard Universitys Sanders Theatre swarmed with students every Tuesday and Thursday."], [["nsubj", "nummod", "advmod", "mwe", "compound", "compound", "acl", "nmod", "case", "amod", "aux", "nmod", "case", "compound", "compound", "acl", "dobj", "compound", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case"], "More than eight hundred Harvard students majoring in different subjects had enrolled in Tal Ben-Shahars course called Positive Psychology to explore the secret of happiness."], [["nsubj", "det", "iobj", "det", "amod", "advmod", "xcomp", "det", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "advmod", "compound:prt", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "amod", "amod", "advcl", "mark", "ccomp", "nsubj", "dobj"], "This course became the most popular one that semester, and Ben-Shahar later went on to publish several best-selling books to help people achieve happiness."], [["advmod", "csubj", "advmod", "mark", "cop", "cop", "nmod", "cc:preconj", "neg", "case", "compound", "cc", "conj", "advmod", "case", "amod", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det"], "Obviously, how to be happy is important not only to Harvard students but also to many other people around the world."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "amod", "cc", "conj", "xcomp", "mark", "dep", "nmod", "case", "det", "appos", "amod", "advmod"], "Indeed, it seems that more and more people begin to feel confined in this fast-paced, increasingly competitive world."], [["nsubj", "aux", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "acl", "mark", "dobj", "amod", "amod"], "Students may come under pressure from their parents to reach high academic standards."], [["nmod", "case", "case", "neg", "advmod", "aux", "nsubj", "xcomp", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "advmod", "dobj", "det", "amod", "acl", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "amod"], "As for adults, not only do many find it challenging to obtain a fulfilling career, but they also have a hard time striking a balance between their work and personal lives."], [["nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "amod", "amod", "acl", "mark", "mwe", "advmod", "mark", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "advmod", "mark", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj", "compound"], "They need to handle many stressful situations, such as how to communicate effectively with their children and how to provide their children with a better living or learning environment."], [["expl", "advmod", "dep", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "aux", "xcomp", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "amod", "amod", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss"], "There is little doubt that happiness has become a burning issue for people in many different stages of their lives."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "dobj", "acl:relcl", "dobj", "nsubj", "nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "nummod", "ccomp", "aux", "nsubj", "xcomp", "dobj", "advmod"], "If we ask Ben-Shahar what happiness is, hell say that happiness is a state we cant arrive at unless we take account of the following three questions: What do we find most meaningful?"], [["nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "What provides us with the most pleasure?"], [["nsubj", "nmod", "case", "cop", "nsubj"], "Finally, what are we good at?"], [["advcl", "mark", "ccomp", "nsubj", "dobj", "nsubj", "dobj", "nummod", "amod"], "To help us find happiness, Ben-Shahar offers six precise tips:"], [["iobj", "dobj", "acl", "mark", "cop"], "Give yourself permission to be human."], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "xcomp", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "We wont feel happy unless we accept all of our emotions, including the negative ones."], [["nmod", "case", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "dobj", "amod", "nmod", "case", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "acl", "mark"], "For students who get low grades at school, its OK to feel disappointed."], [["nsubj", "xcomp", "xcomp", "mark", "ccomp", "advmod", "nsubj", "dobj", "det:predet", "det"], "We dont have to suppress how we feel all the time."], [["dobj", "compound", "cc", "conj", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "iobj", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "nmod", "case"], "Do work and other activities that give you pleasure and provide you with meaning."], [["csubj", "nmod", "case", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "cop", "advmod", "cc", "conj", "aux", "iobj", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case"], "Engaging in activities that are personally significant and enjoyable can bring us a lot of pleasure."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "xcomp", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound"], "If you like to travel and entertain people with stories, try working as a tour guide."], [["nsubj", "aux", "xcomp", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "cc", "dep", "advmod", "ccomp", "nsubj", "aux", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "cop", "cc", "conj", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss"], "You may find your job interesting, and, most importantly, you may find that you are confident and professional in your work."], [["nsubj", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case"], "Happiness depends mostly on your state of mind."], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case", "amod", "cc:preconj", "cc", "conj"], "Ben-Shahar states that our happiness stems from both positive and negative experiences."], [["ccomp", "nsubj", "det", "dobj", "nmod:poss"], "Suppose a man loses his job."], [["nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "acl", "mark", "dobj", "det", "amod"], "He can view it as a catastrophe, or he can think positively and take it as an opportunity to get a better job."], [["dobj", "nmod:poss", "amod"], "Simplify your daily tasks."], [["nsubjpass", "aux", "auxpass", "advcl", "mark", "advcl", "advmod", "advmod"], "Happiness can be found in avoiding doing too much."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "amod", "compound:prt", "nmod:tmod", "nummod"], "Dont pack excess activities into one day."], [["advmod", "dep", "dobj", "neg", "amod", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "nsubj", "cc", "conj", "csubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "amod", "advmod", "aux", "dobj"], "Usually, theres not enough time to finish everything we list, and failing to complete the tasks as planned can frustrate us."], [["dobj", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss"], "Pay attention to your body."], [["advcl", "advmod", "cop", "conj", "cc", "conj", "advmod", "nsubj", "aux", "compound:prt", "xcomp", "dobj", "nmod:poss"], "When were tired, hungry, or physically inactive, we may end up compromising our happiness."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "conj", "dobj", "amod", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "amod", "advcl", "mark", "xcomp", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "cop", "dep", "cc", "conj", "advmod"], "Thus, we should exercise regularly, get enough sleep, and eat balanced meals to make sure that we are both physically and mentally healthy."], [["acl", "advcl", "advmod"], "Express gratitude, whenever possible."], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "nmod", "case", "nsubj", "aux"], "Dont take what you have for granted."], [["xcomp", "mark", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "advmod", "nmod:npmod", "det", "nmod", "case", "det"], "Learn to appreciate and relish the wonderful things in lifeeven just a smile from a stranger."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "compound", "dobj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "amod", "cop", "det", "nmod", "case"], "Apparently, Ben-Shahars advice shows us that positive thinking is the key to happiness."], [["nsubj", "aux", "cop", "compound", "compound", "nmod", "case", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "det", "amod", "compound", "cc", "conj", "csubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "advmod"], "It can be something largethe feeling of joy upon winning a big sports competition; or smallgetting satisfaction from a task finally completed."], [["advmod", "nmod:npmod", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "amod", "advmod", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "mark", "xcomp", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "mark", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "nsubj", "advmod", "aux", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "case", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case"], "Whats more, its also important for us to stop envying what others have and to focus on what we alone can take pleasure in during our search for happiness."], [["nsubj", "nummod", "aux", "dobj", "acl:relcl", "aux", "cop", "det", "amod", "compound"], "One thing is clearfinding happiness can be a joyous lifetime pursuit."]]